# Raw SLP/SLD bytes are served from the self-hosted Garage S3 buckets via the
# Worker. Keeping local sample files under testgraphics/ during development is
# fine; committing them is not.
public/gif/testgraphics/slp/*.slp
public/gif/testgraphics/sld/*.sld